WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.869
Good morning, family. I'm excited to be

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:05.630
with you all again today. Look at

00:00:05.640 --> 00:00:08.830
this. This is our prayer. This is

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:11.150
what we were interceding for last night.

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:12.990
Whenever we were praying,

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:14.350
there wasn't even rain in the

00:00:14.360 --> 00:00:17.830
forecast, and all of a sudden,

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:19.710
it just started

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:23.150
raining. I could hear the thunder, and

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:25.830
we got almost an inch of rain.

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:28.109
This is supernatural

00:00:28.119 --> 00:00:30.870
rain, ladies and gentlemen. When you pray

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:34.950
and you believe, all things are possible

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:38.470
to him that believes—even the weather.

00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:40.510
I

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:42.190
just wanted to come on here; I'm

00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:43.510
excited about it. I wanted to

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.830
show you what

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:47.350
happens when you believe God for

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:49.830
something. Rain is a

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:52.310
big deal for us because it's been really

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:54.270
dry. I just thought,

00:00:54.270 --> 00:00:54.280
'I

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:57.430
wanted to come on

00:00:57.440 --> 00:01:00.509
and show you our prayers are

00:01:00.509 --> 00:01:00.519
working.'It's

00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:03.310
amazing for the farmers, for

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:05.750
the drought, for all of it.

00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:07.469
We're going to believe some more tonight.

00:01:07.479 --> 00:01:09.390
I asked the Lord for three inches, but we

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:11.749
almost got an inch. It's a

00:01:11.759 --> 00:01:14.830
work in progress. Sometimes

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:17.469
you see the olive branch

00:01:17.479 --> 00:01:19.429
and the dove's beak

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:21.510
before you get the full manifestation.

00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:24.550
Like Noah, he sent the dove out

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.670
and it brought back an olive branch,

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:29.109
showing him the flood was over,

00:01:29.119 --> 00:01:31.469
the storm was over. I'm telling

00:01:31.479 --> 00:01:33.590
you, that's the way it will be in your life.

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:40.670
Believe God. Even if you

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:43.910
see first the blade, then the ear, then

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:47.510
the full manifestation, never give up on

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:49.950
what you're believing for. You may see

00:01:49.960 --> 00:01:51.870
just a little bit of something, just like

00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:54.709
I saw almost an inch, but I'm believing

00:01:54.719 --> 00:01:57.550
God for over three inches. I want to go four or

00:01:57.550 --> 00:01:57.560
five inches

00:01:57.560 --> 00:01:59.190
to break the drought so that

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:02.389
we're not in one anymore. These

00:02:02.389 --> 00:02:02.399
are

00:02:02.399 --> 00:02:05.830
exciting times. I have

00:02:05.840 --> 00:02:08.869
such an expectation in my spirit

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:11.510
today. There's a stirring inside of

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:12.949
me; something is happening in the

00:02:12.959 --> 00:02:15.550
realm of the spirit as we're praying

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:18.830
together. I can feel it. Tonight,

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:20.550
when I was sitting there talking to

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.790
the Lord, I felt

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:25.390
a fire, like when

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:27.509
you're stoking a fireplace.

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:31.309
I can feel it turning. I

00:02:31.309 --> 00:02:31.319
said,

00:02:31.319 --> 00:02:33.350
'Holy Spirit, there's

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:36.390
something going

00:02:36.390 --> 00:02:36.400
on.'We're

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:38.190
moving the mountain, y'all.

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:42.470
Faith will move a mountain. The

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:47.750
Bible says it in Mark 11:23

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:47.760
and

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:50.190
24: 'Whatsoever things you

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:52.070
desire, when you pray, believe that you

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:54.350
receive them, and you shall have them.

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:56.509
If you say to the mountain,

00:02:56.519 --> 00:02:58.430
"Be thou removed and be thou cast into

00:02:58.430 --> 00:02:58.440
the sea,"and

00:02:58.440 --> 00:02:59.990
shall not doubt in your heart,

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.110
you shall have whatsoever things you

00:03:03.110 --> 00:03:03.120
say.'I

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.270
want to encourage you all:

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:07.589
don't give up on what you're believing

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:10.190
for.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:12.710
When I was praying this

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:14.869
evening, the Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you

00:03:14.879 --> 00:03:16.750
to tell those old testimonies you've

00:03:16.760 --> 00:03:19.470
told before.'I told you all

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:22.390
a couple of videos ago about the dog being

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:25.550
raised from the dead and my little girl

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:27.990
praying for that dog in the hall.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:29.910
All things are possible to him

00:03:29.910 --> 00:03:29.920
who

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:32.190
believes.

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:33.990
I'm going

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:35.990
to tell you another testimony of what

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:39.509
happened to me.

00:03:39.519 --> 00:03:43.589
I was mowing my grandmother's

00:03:43.599 --> 00:03:45.869
yard—I

00:03:45.879 --> 00:03:48.789
mowed

00:03:48.799 --> 00:03:51.350
her

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:53.030
grass all the

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:55.830
time—and

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:57.470
there was this African-American man

00:03:57.480 --> 00:03:59.990
walking down the road. He would

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.869
walk a couple

00:04:01.869 --> 00:04:01.879
of

00:04:01.879 --> 00:04:05.789
feet and stop,

00:04:05.799 --> 00:04:08.229
breathing really hard.

00:04:08.239 --> 00:04:10.750
I thought, 'Wow, that's

00:04:10.750 --> 00:04:10.760
sad,'but

00:04:10.760 --> 00:04:12.350
I just kept mowing.

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.710
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to

00:04:13.720 --> 00:04:16.550
go pray for that man.'I said, 'You want

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:19.069
me to go pray for that

00:04:19.069 --> 00:04:19.079
man?'I

00:04:19.079 --> 00:04:21.590
ignored it, to be real

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.629
with y'all. I

00:04:23.629 --> 00:04:23.639
thought,

00:04:23.639 --> 00:04:24.830
'I don't know that man; I'm not going to

00:04:24.840 --> 00:04:27.350
go pray for

00:04:27.350 --> 00:04:27.360
him.'I

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:29.029
just

00:04:29.039 --> 00:04:31.029
started mowing some more. He got closer, and the Lord

00:04:31.039 --> 00:04:32.990
said, 'Are you going to obey me and go pray for that man?'I reasoned it out in my mind, thinking that man probably wouldn't want me praying for him. That's your flesh trying

00:04:32.990 --> 00:04:33.000
to talk you out of

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:34.510
it through fear or

00:04:34.510 --> 00:04:34.520
intimidation. The devil tries to

00:04:34.520 --> 00:04:36.550
whisper in your ear to

00:04:36.550 --> 00:04:36.560
discourage you. The man

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:39.070
got right

00:04:39.070 --> 00:04:39.080
up

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:42.469
to

00:04:42.469 --> 00:04:42.479
me,

00:04:42.479 --> 00:04:45.150
and the Lord said sternly, 'Are you going

00:04:45.160 --> 00:04:47.189
to obey me and go pray for that

00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:09.670
man?'I

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:40.950
said, 'Father, I'm sorry. I'll go

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:44.110
pray for him.'I

00:05:44.110 --> 00:05:44.120
turned

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:47.189
the mower off and

00:05:47.199 --> 00:05:50.790
said, 'Sir, can I talk to

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:53.790
you for a second?'He stopped

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:56.070
and looked at me. I noticed

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:59.230
his skin was ashy.

00:06:02.160 --> 00:06:05.790
He looked

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:08.830
very pale

00:06:08.830 --> 00:06:08.840
and

00:06:08.840 --> 00:06:15.589
gray, not healthy.

00:06:15.599 --> 00:06:18.110
He had tubes in his nose and

00:06:19.639 --> 00:06:22.270
an oxygen tank he was dragging

00:06:22.280 --> 00:06:24.510
behind

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:27.550
him.

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:29.110
I

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:30.550
asked,

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:32.670
'How are you doing today?'He

00:06:32.670 --> 00:06:32.680
said,

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:36.950
'I'm not doing good. I'm dying.'I asked what the problem was. He said,

00:06:46.840 --> 00:06:49.230
'I need a lung transplant. I sprayed

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:53.189
Roundup for the government for 38 years,

00:06:55.919 --> 00:06:58.749
and it

00:06:58.759 --> 00:07:02.469
ruined my lungs.

00:07:02.479 --> 00:07:06.629
I'm on the

00:07:06.629 --> 00:07:06.639
donor

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:11.230
list. The doctors say if I

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:14.390
don't get these lungs, I'm going to

00:07:14.390 --> 00:07:14.400
die.'I

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.629
asked,

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:20.150
'Do you

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:23.270
believe

00:07:28.199 --> 00:07:30.670
Jesus

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:33.029
will heal

00:07:33.039 --> 00:07:34.909
you?'He

00:07:34.919 --> 00:07:36.230
just shook his head,

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:37.510
looking

00:07:37.520 --> 00:07:39.990
dumbfounded.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.830
He didn't give me a

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:43.589
straight answer;

00:07:43.599 --> 00:07:45.350
he

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:47.469
just looked at

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:51.710
the ground. I

00:07:51.710 --> 00:07:51.720
asked,

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:54.670
'Can I lay hands on you?'He looked

00:07:54.670 --> 00:07:54.680
at me

00:07:54.680 --> 00:07:56.790
like

00:07:58.159 --> 00:08:00.350
I

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:02.350
was weirding him out. I

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:04.309
said,

00:08:04.319 --> 00:08:06.670
'I can just pray for you,'and he

00:08:06.670 --> 00:08:06.680
said that was

00:08:06.680 --> 00:08:08.309
fine,

00:08:08.319 --> 00:08:09.629
I could touch his

00:08:09.639 --> 00:08:12.469
shoulder.

00:08:12.479 --> 00:08:15.469
I put my hand on his shoulder and said,

00:08:15.479 --> 00:08:17.830
'I'm

00:08:17.840 --> 00:08:19.390
going to say a

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:20.790
prayer for you and we're going to

00:08:20.800 --> 00:08:23.950
believe God. I believe

00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:26.309
with all my heart that today you're

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:28.830
going to get healed because Jesus told me

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:33.790
to pray for

00:08:36.909 --> 00:08:36.919
you.'I

00:08:40.519 --> 00:08:43.389
said, 'I

00:08:43.399 --> 00:08:47.430
speak to your lungs to be healed in the

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:51.150
name of Jesus, and I command new lungs to

00:08:51.160 --> 00:08:54.630
go inside your body.'I didn't ask;

00:08:54.640 --> 00:08:58.509
I commanded

00:08:58.519 --> 00:08:59.990
them.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:01.829
I

00:09:01.839 --> 00:09:03.829
touched his chest and said,

00:09:03.839 --> 00:09:06.829
'I

00:09:06.839 --> 00:09:09.310
command you to be healed and I command

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:12.150
new lungs to come back into your

00:09:12.150 --> 00:09:12.160
body.'I

00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:16.550
didn't feel

00:09:16.550 --> 00:09:16.560
anything.

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.790
I thought it was like touching a cold

00:09:19.800 --> 00:09:23.509
stove.

00:09:23.519 --> 00:09:25.470
I said, 'I

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:27.790
believe you're healed. Have a blessed day.'He

00:09:27.790 --> 00:09:27.800
thanked me and walked away.

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:29.430
I said,

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:40.389
'Lord, I obeyed

00:09:40.399 --> 00:09:43.190
you. Now it's your

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:49.310
job.'About

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:57.230
a week

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:59.470
later,

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:01.710
this

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:05.230
man ran up to me in the

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:08.430
yard.

00:10:08.440 --> 00:10:11.150
I did not

00:10:11.160 --> 00:10:13.030
recognize him.

00:10:15.480 --> 00:10:20.110
He said, 'Sir, do you

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:23.949
remember me?'I said, 'No, I've never

00:10:23.959 --> 00:10:26.910
seen you

00:10:26.910 --> 00:10:26.920
before.'He

00:10:26.920 --> 00:10:29.829
said, 'I'm the man you prayed

00:10:29.829 --> 00:10:29.839
for!'I

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:32.750
said,

00:10:32.760 --> 00:10:36.629
'My goodness, sir,

00:10:36.639 --> 00:10:39.750
look at you!'His skin was completely

00:10:39.760 --> 00:10:42.750
normal. He

00:10:42.760 --> 00:10:44.750
had color back in

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:48.150
his skin and looked healthy.

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:54.590
He said, 'I was

00:10:54.600 --> 00:10:57.910
healed when you prayed for me. I

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:01.350
went back to the doctor, and the doctor asked what I did. He said I

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:14.030
have

00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:29.710
two

00:11:29.710 --> 00:11:29.720
brand-new

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:33.590
lungs.'They

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:37.190
took him

00:11:37.200 --> 00:11:40.030
off the

00:11:40.030 --> 00:11:40.040
donor

00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:42.949
list. He had no

00:11:42.959 --> 00:11:47.150
oxygen tank and was walking around normally.

00:11:47.150 --> 00:11:47.160
He came

00:11:47.160 --> 00:11:50.150
back to

00:11:50.160 --> 00:11:52.990
thank

00:11:52.990 --> 00:11:53.000
me.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:55.550
We

00:11:55.550 --> 00:11:55.560
eventually

00:11:55.560 --> 00:11:57.590
led him to Jesus.

00:11:57.600 --> 00:12:00.150
He

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:03.069
used

00:12:03.079 --> 00:12:06.230
to

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:08.590
walk

00:12:08.600 --> 00:12:10.590
around the

00:12:10.590 --> 00:12:10.600
neighborhood

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:12.990
fast

00:12:17.760 --> 00:12:19.230
with his little cane.

00:12:20.639 --> 00:12:23.509
He wanted

00:12:23.519 --> 00:12:25.829
peaches, so I gave

00:12:25.839 --> 00:12:27.430
him some from my trees. It was

00:12:29.920 --> 00:12:32.030
an

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:37.710
amazing testimony. But

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:42.590
after a period of

00:12:42.590 --> 00:12:42.600
time—this

00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:46.710
went on for a

00:12:46.710 --> 00:12:46.720
few

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:49.509
years—he

00:12:49.519 --> 00:12:53.150
started walking slow

00:12:53.160 --> 00:12:56.870
again. He got that ashy look

00:12:56.870 --> 00:12:56.880
and

00:12:56.880 --> 00:13:00.590
the

00:13:00.590 --> 00:13:00.600
tubes

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:02.790
in his nose

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:06.949
again.

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:13.949
What I'm trying to say is you

00:13:13.959 --> 00:13:17.470
can get a healing,

00:13:19.959 --> 00:13:23.629
but if you don't get a foundation

00:13:23.629 --> 00:13:23.639
in

00:13:23.639 --> 00:13:27.670
the Word of God, the enemy comes back.

00:13:27.670 --> 00:13:27.680
The Bible

00:13:27.680 --> 00:13:30.710
says he goes away for a

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:33.230
season,

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:35.269
but he

00:13:35.269 --> 00:13:35.279
returns

00:13:35.279 --> 00:13:38.550
to the house he came from.

00:13:52.279 --> 00:13:55.829
If you don't have the Word

00:13:55.839 --> 00:13:59.710
inside you to know that 'by His

00:13:59.720 --> 00:14:02.629
stripes you are healed,'when the

00:14:02.629 --> 00:14:02.639
devil tries

00:14:02.639 --> 00:14:05.269
to bring that sickness back,

00:14:05.279 --> 00:14:07.430
you have to

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:11.189
resist

00:14:11.189 --> 00:14:11.199
him.

00:14:11.199 --> 00:14:14.350
You have

00:14:20.560 --> 00:14:23.389
to stand

00:14:23.399 --> 00:14:27.030
and say,

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:29.870
'I am not accepting your

00:14:29.870 --> 00:14:29.880
poo-poo

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:31.710
package on my front porch

00:14:33.160 --> 00:14:37.990
again.'If

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:41.189
you don't have a

00:14:41.199 --> 00:14:43.389
foundation,

00:14:43.389 --> 00:14:43.399
you

00:14:43.399 --> 00:14:45.710
can't

00:14:45.710 --> 00:14:45.720
keep

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:48.990
your

00:14:49.000 --> 00:14:51.749
healing.

00:14:53.560 --> 00:14:57.269
You

00:15:00.480 --> 00:15:02.350
need

00:15:04.560 --> 00:15:08.269
a root of the Word deep

00:15:08.269 --> 00:15:08.279
in

00:15:08.279 --> 00:15:10.749
your heart so that when the devil

00:15:10.759 --> 00:15:13.069
comes

00:15:13.069 --> 00:15:13.079
like

00:15:13.079 --> 00:15:16.949
a roaring lion,

00:15:16.959 --> 00:15:19.670
you say,

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:22.389
'You're not coming back on my

00:15:29.189 --> 00:15:29.199
land.'Great

00:15:33.839 --> 00:15:37.550
healing miracles and

00:15:37.560 --> 00:15:41.749
demonstrations of the Spirit are coming.

00:15:41.759 --> 00:15:44.509
Many

00:15:44.519 --> 00:15:47.110
of you will be healed,

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:50.189
but the only

00:15:50.199 --> 00:15:53.389
